episodes.title: The Interview
episodes.description: Mr. Chopp Chopp, a successful podcaster, bought a nail salon. His idea of a successful nail shop would be run by men, so he hires Klepto and Two-Braids as manicurists. The nail shop struggles to maintain and Mr. Chopp comes up with various hustles.
episodes.cast: Aman Royal,Dwayne Wayne,Malik Johnson,Mylani Royal,Tiffany Smith
